                "name": "Mindshock",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "Whenever a grioth damages a creature with a psychic weapon, a surge of violent psychic energy pulses into the victim\u2019s body, causing an additional 1d4 points of nonlethal damage. On a confirmed critical hit, this additional nonlethal damage does not increase, but the creature struck must succeed at a DC 13 Will save or become confused for 1d2 rounds. This is a mind-affecting effect. The save DC is Charisma-based and includes a +2 racial bonus."
